snippet.title: Chronicle: RuneScape Legends Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download now on Steam! : http://bit.ly/ChronicleOnSteamYT

Play with the fate of Legends in a battle of wits, strategy and combat, where lives are gambled on the turn of your cards. Leave your minions behind as you fight your own battles, expand and master your deck, and face the challenge of unique card combat. 

Chronicle is a new kind of card gaming experience.

Follow us:
https://twitter.com/RSChronicle
https://www.facebook.com/RSChronicle/
https://www.twitch.tv/rschronicle
